Package: kowabunga-kahuna
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Kowabunga Kahuna Orchestrator
 Kowabunga stands for 'Kvm Orchestrator With A BUNch of Goods Added'.
 Kahuna is the core service engine, providing REST API frontend and orchestration capabilities.

Package: kowabunga-kaktus-agent
Architecture: any
